{"tid":409381,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高路普：雙曼領放令壓力更大","createTime":"2017-09-22T04:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T05:25:13.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a61c0bf13628ae82c31d6a8c8d401bd747ab81f9","tid":409381,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"利物浦領隊高路普相信，兩支曼徹斯特球隊曼聯和曼城在季初跑出，令開季不算順遂的利記處境更為突出，但他仍對麾下球員投以信任一票，認為紅軍可以從「出閘脫腳」及英格蘭聯賽盃早早出局的情況中反彈過來。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦最近在各項賽事連續四場不勝，當中更輸了兩場。紅軍現時落後榜首的曼聯和曼城五分，但高路普強調他仍未陷入驚慌的地步：「執教每支球隊，外界都一定有期望，只是在晏菲路的情況更甚。顯然的在利物浦大家認為球隊是要贏得聯賽冠軍的，即使在過去25年沒有贏過，情況都沒有變。特別是當兩支曼徹斯特球隊都有不錯表現的時候，情況就變的更加困難，但我無法改變這一切。」<br />\n<br />\n高路普續道：「我只能和球隊繼續去做對的事，也在其他地方繼續進步，現實就是這樣。你們真的以為我會就此感到慌亂嗎？這就是足球，我們有八分在手，有四場比賽我們是明顯較好的一隊，但卻未能獲得相應的成績。我不感到慌張，因為我不能想像有人會這樣想。」"},{"pid":"cdcbb0a12a8eecd8efcb432af09334c2e9743ca8","tid":409381,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"領先一球總是很危險"},{"pid":"a30978cf0bddfd7a53b31fd617542d8cb4822daf","tid":409381,"uid":5163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"死廢中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲利狗點解可以咁厚面皮"},{"pid":"2c78fa117380d224f4fe0257ae155a6a9c48b926","tid":409381,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:29:55.000Z","msg":"原來利記失分係玩政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dde1f9b84e85c1d0c5ccaa9880c93c82d2a005b","tid":409381,"uid":113682,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"算數啦<br />\n一個淨係得一種熱血迫搶既教頭教一隊淨係識買2線既垃圾波<br />\n可以爭d咩?"},{"pid":"6633dce15ce8433110afb721bb30cf99c5b49218","tid":409381,"uid":759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算數啦<br />\n一個淨係得一種熱血迫搶既教頭教一隊淨係識買2線既垃圾波<br />\n可以爭d咩?</blockquote><br />\n呢兩隊根本只有左右邊隊奪冠既能力<br />\n但並無奪冠既能力<br />\n係d 垃圾球迷日日打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f396fe07500f9bb2756f5f5dd9f7b1a6d2c971","tid":409381,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"樓上幾個回覆做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地講緊自己好大壓力喎"},{"pid":"70be9b758e58b83540b79e90d6ebfbabf57937e7","tid":409381,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/21686319_1637792489624774_736535586142321855_n.jpg?oh=06a79fc5dfefa4584d0aecd2f213ebfd&amp;oe=5A3A9EF9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F21686319_1637792489624774_736535586142321855_n.jpg%3Foh%3D06a79fc5dfefa4584d0aecd2f213ebfd%26oe%3D5A3A9EF9&h=4ef3ff53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ca219e4ab932619a37861c2e8d7f1717cb8e59c","tid":409381,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"點解羅渣士會俾人炒，高普仲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40e00524885152d56ac5bb16834f072ee864891","tid":409381,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"皇馬都未有壓力"},{"pid":"e8d887cdecab7ebc2d1516006b15f360d7080a41","tid":409381,"uid":113682,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上幾個回覆做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地講緊自己好大壓力喎</blockquote><br />\n做乜鳩?<br />\n笑柒傻鳩痢講到佢有份爭咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b4a58ecdab2773a586c1383b1c12f264cf0f75","tid":409381,"uid":119157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi