能想像有人會這樣想。」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00887e5211d65e6a4b56337296960bc1dd7acb17","tid":409381,"uid":28378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"李城做壞個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}